mber":1386,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"central district 中心区","headword":"central district"},{"type":"entry","text":"residential unit 住宅单元，居住单元","headword":"residential unit"},{"type":"entry","text":"stair [steə(r)]","headword":"stair"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.楼梯；阶梯"},{"type":"text","text":"step [step]"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.台阶"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"}]},{"number":1387,"blocks":[{"type":"example","text":"A：I know the housing price there. The house is worth a fortune.（我"},{"type":"text","text":"了解那里的房价。这房子值不少钱呢。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：You bet. It is a central district.（肯定的。那是个中心区。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：Why do you still invest in the real estate market?（你为什么还要"},{"type":"text","text":"投资房地产市场？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Because the price of houses will continue to rise.（因为房产价格"},{"type":"text","text":"还会继续上涨。）"}]}]}